{"tid":1707639,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今日藍屍叔一燒事件嚇怕了一眾準備出黎搞連儂牆嘅廢老","createTime":"2019-11-11T10:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T10:56:54.000Z","uid":264192,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"10ac3dc898c62388d557a94d73977245edff39f3","tid":1707639,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">諗下以前幾多單藍絲在連儂牆打人殺人，然後仲大搖大擺咁離開，搞到好多藍屍見到都想有樣學樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍屍廢老就係睇死你班後生無膽反抗，而我地的確好多時會選擇硬食，就係為左要搶佔道德高地。但搶佔左道德高地又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，往往要用身體去換noise，值得咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好喇，今日班藍屍終於見到叔一燒事件，真係嚇到啤一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估個個藍屍都想攞條命出黎? 咪傻啦大部分都只係想搵黃絲做出氣袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到底今次叔一燒事件的確係殺雞焉用牛刀，送左粒子彈比對面。但倒轉黎睇其實係大大增加左藍屍廢老出黎搞事嘅成本，無形中其實減輕左連儂牆手足嘅壓力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不割蓆</span>"},{"pid":"d00d0feb77da2fa023a53c60b76334fb4c2b533e","tid":1707639,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:51:41.000Z","msg":"子彈？佢地班仆街就係真射左子彈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3fd86be39c3f74ac238eecc21d835098632a64","tid":1707639,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"466570412a9afa41e89b386b708c6a7ffa4a5121","tid":1707639,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:55:22.000Z","msg":"破窗效應，自從神獸出左少左好多廢老出黎，依家再燒一燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84549b9bb2f758700668af9f4bff91bdcae021db","tid":1707639,"uid":59736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:56:54.000Z","msg":"但手足都要小心<br />\n呢d招藍屍都